OL,3,CThousands gather at Stonehenge to mark
OL,4,Csummer solstice
OL,6,FThousands of people watched the sun
OL,7,Frise over Stonehenge to celebrate the
OL,8,Fsummer solstice, signifying the end of
OL,9,Fspring.
OL,11,FThose who gathered for the spectacle
OL,12,Fon Sunday at the neolithic monument in
OL,13,FWiltshire had a warm start to the
OL,14,Fmorning as they marked the year's
OL,15,Flongest day.
OL,17,FThe sunrise was livestreamed by
OL,18,FEnglish Heritage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
