OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782043873
OL,3,CThousands gather at Stonehenge to mark
OL,4,Csummer solstice
OL,6,FTemperatures in Salisbury reached
OL,7,F13.5C by 4am, according to the Met
OL,8,FOffice, making it a pleasant start to
OL,9,Fwhat is expected to be a very hot day.
OL,11,FThere were cheers as the sun rose at
OL,12,F4.25am, marking the official start of
OL,13,Fastronomical summer.
OL,15,FStonehenge is a monument built on the
OL,16,Falignment of the midsummer sunrise and
OL,17,Fthe midwinter sunset.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
