OL,3,CThousands gather at Stonehenge to mark
OL,4,Csummer solstice
OL,6,FThis year the exact moment of solstice
OL,7,Fwas 9.24am
OL,9,FGeorgia Butters, English Heritage's
OL,10,FHead of Stonehenge, said: "There was a
OL,11,Ftruly gorgeous sunrise at Stonehenge
OL,12,Fthis year ` and it was a really
OL,13,Fmemorable occasion.
OL,15,F"Coming together at this iconic
OL,16,Fmonument for the Summer Solstice is a
OL,17,Ftradition that brings people together
OL,18,Ffrom near and far.
OL,26,@rD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
